    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "养由基"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "自幼生来八字差，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到处奔驰走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺养由基，乃远阳人氏。在罗泊帐下，当了一名步卒。可恨那贼，目不识人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是俺逃出营来，闻听斗越椒，在朝谋反，杀了司马蒍贾。带领人马，搜宫杀院。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "庄王回朝，出下榜文，招聚天下英雄。乃是俺好汉出头之日也。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要为天下奇男子，须在世间立大功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时运不至困豪家，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罗泊看俺是小娃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "下海拴龙何足夸。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要与皇王定邦家。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 5,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": null,
        "musical_styles": []
