    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "养由基",
        "楚庄王",
        "此乃是孤王的洪福大",
        "眼前若有千岁令",
        "营门揭榜如戏耍",
        "越椒他是英雄将",
        "龙套甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楚庄王、四龙套同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昨日阵前把仗打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "越椒放箭射孤家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "险些一命丧黄沙。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旌旃飘渺两眼花。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蛟龙无水困浅沙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "时运不至走天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "见了大王把话答。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "营门揭榜如戏耍"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！你这小将，有何本领，擅揭黄榜！"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相烦通禀：就说养由基求见大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "候着。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：营门外有一小将揭榜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "命他进来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "龙套甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将呢，大王命你进见，须要小心了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王在上，小人叩头。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将家住哪里，姓甚名谁，有何本领，敢揭孤的黄榜？"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人养由基，乃远阳人氏。自幼学习一十八般武艺，件件皆能。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那斗越椒，甚是骁勇，你敢前去对敌？"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一颗明珠土内藏，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "数载未曾放毫光。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "铁打的金钢碍何妨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "管叫逆贼丧无常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "越椒他是英雄将"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼前若有千岁令"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那贼子恶箭伤人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人能射凤凰夺窝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何为凤凰夺窝？"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小人能射五箭，箭劈箭杆。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王不信，下帐演来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王帐内把令传下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看视某家演箭法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一见小将喜气发，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "亚赛当年小哪吒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看视小将演箭法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楚庄王上高坡，坐。养由基上，射。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两手弓开如月牙，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "射转乾坤定邦家。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怪不得小将把口夸，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "凤凰夺窝果不差。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天遣小将把贼拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你用什么兵器？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "此乃是孤王的洪福大"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "青铜刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，耍来孤王观看。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基耍刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉王旨意把刀耍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "困龙从此襄天涯。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "定把越椒父子拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基耍刀。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不要耍了。孤王赐你银盔银甲，命你大战斗越椒。快走快走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "养由基",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（养由基下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤王帐内把令发，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大小三军听根芽："
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只等小将把贼拿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将他九族尽灭正孤的王法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楚庄王、四龙套同下。）"
        }
      ],
